  "3292290": {
    "name": "肥羊危机II",
    "steam_appid": 3292290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的职业，数量众多的装备，不同种类的敌人。这是一款 Roguelite 轻度休闲游戏，游戏内杀敌到达一定次数会随机切换职业，每个职业有多种变异体，每种变异体技能各有差异。可以孤军奋战，也可叫上好友或加入其他玩家房间共同并肩作战。体验不同职业，体会超多技能，探索隐藏内容，搭配最适合自己的装备，击败最终BOSS，享受组队合作共同通关的乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>------------------------------职业------------------------------</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内拥有数量众多的职业供你游玩，每个职业拥有15种变异体，每种变异体技能拥有不同的强化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/c431d5fd7e5caa373dd033798e0b9953.poster.avif?t=1732254591\" width=640 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/c431d5fd7e5caa373dd033798e0b9953.webm?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/c431d5fd7e5caa373dd033798e0b9953.mp4?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>------------------------------操作------------------------------</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作简单，只需要上下左右，人物朝向跟随鼠标移动。每局游戏30分钟，快速体验，节奏紧凑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/fd920f3511f312effbc860e07e3af69c.poster.avif?t=1732254591\" width=640 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/fd920f3511f312effbc860e07e3af69c.webm?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/fd920f3511f312effbc860e07e3af69c.mp4?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>------------------------------联机------------------------------</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以孤军奋战，也可叫上好友或加入其他玩家房间共同并肩作战。只要还有一人存活游戏就能无限复活！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/dab8841e4fe10cadfc75f63c2e763e31.poster.avif?t=1732254591\" width=640 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/dab8841e4fe10cadfc75f63c2e763e31.webm?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/dab8841e4fe10cadfc75f63c2e763e31.mp4?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>------------------------------玩法------------------------------</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击杀敌人获得金币，可以在商店购买装备，装备可以通过合成变得更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/84d632773f771d7739926d9ac25229ef.poster.avif?t=1732254591\" width=640 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/84d632773f771d7739926d9ac25229ef.webm?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/84d632773f771d7739926d9ac25229ef.mp4?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>------------------------------插件系统------------------------------</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏通关后可以获得与游戏难度相等的插件点数，这些点数可以用来解锁和升级插件，插件可以有效的增强自身战力，不同的插件提供不同的效果<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/626d3b597bb835b164ca7079fd532207.poster.avif?t=1732254591\" width=640 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/626d3b597bb835b164ca7079fd532207.webm?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292290/extras/626d3b597bb835b164ca7079fd532207.mp4?t=1732254591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
